Name: Therapist
Text: So, in conclusion, he just run away from you in a circles and hid in bushes?

Name: Therapist
Text: That's a bit lame tactic, if you'd ask me.

Name: Bieda
Text: Okey, okey, you're my therapist. Stop dissing me.

Name: Bieda
Text: After all of that, I started misleading him, coming from behind and running after him.

Name: Therapist
Text: Let's continue, and remember to talk about your feelings.
